column1:
So I heard you guys were waiting for me to get
back?
You guys're surprisingly particular, you know?

It's the first calling card we're sendin' out since
you joined. Figured you'd wanna be there for it.

Well, it's not like I haven't helped out with one
already. It doesn't seem like that big a deal...
That's why we have a little proposal for you. Why don't you write this one, Zenkichi-san?
Me!? But I've never written one before!

Yes, we should all be more open to new
experiences.
Yeah, but I don't think I want to...

Yes, remember what Konoe did to Akane. You
simply need to express your rage.
Well, it's true he does have to answer for that...

All right, that takes care of the calling card. Now
we just gotta figure out how to send it.
Hey, I didn't agree to anything...

If he's so comfortable badmouthing us on TV,
maybe it's time we gave him a taste of his own
medicine.
Could we just hand-deliver it, maybe?
If we wanna get arrested, yeah...
Let's go with the TV idea.

Hmm... I don't know. I'm not sensing a clear
winner here.
You don't see them very often nowadays.

That's the Regenbogen. It's the only airship in
Japan that's currently in service.

It seems it's being used to advertise EMMA for
Madicce at the moment.
Apparently, it circles Osaka's airspace every day.
